snippet.title: Zodiac Revenger Trailer
snippet.description:
Zodiac Revenger is a 2D action platformer. Took place post the Zodiac race, the 12 winners have been reward with great mystical power. They used it to spread chaos throught the peaceful land. Follow the Cat on a quest to dethrone the terror rulers, and get his own revenge on the Zodiac leader.

Add to steam wishlist: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2663670/Zodiac_Revenger/
